{"type":"ScenarioReference","class":"Mythos","tokens":{"front":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, discard the top 3 cards of the encounter deck. If you discarded 1 or more <t>Hazard</t> cards, choose 1 and draw it."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. X is the number of locations adjacent to your location."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If this token is revealed during an investigation test, lose 1 action."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. If you fail, swap your location with an adjacent revealed location."}},"back":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. If you fail, discard the top 4 cards of the encounter deck. If you discarded 1 or more <t>Hazard</t> or <t>Scheme</t> cards, choose 1 and draw it."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. X is one more than the number of locations adjacent to your location."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. If this token is revealed during an investigation test, end your turn."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. Swap your location with an adjacent revealed location."}}},"TtsZoopGuid":"c488369e-6d22-4a78-a4cb-ae6a9a2c60ec"}
